Performance Optimization"
Goal: Make it blazing fast
Tasks:
Task 1: Image Optimization Deep Dive

Optimize all images:
- Convert to WebP format
- Use responsive images with srcset
- Lazy load below-fold images
- Blur placeholder data URLs
- Priority loading for hero image

Task 2: Code Splitting

Optimize bundle:
- Dynamic imports for heavy components
- Split portfolio modal into separate chunk
- Lazy load Framer Motion animations
- Use next/dynamic for client components


Task 3: Caching Strategy

Implement proper caching:
- Static generation for main page
- Incremental static regeneration for portfolio
- Cache portfolio data
- Service worker for offline (optional)

Task 4: Performance Audit

Run and fix:
- Lighthouse audit (target 95+ on all)
- Core Web Vitals optimization
- Reduce JavaScript bundle size
- Minimize CSS
- Check mobile performance